A desklet to display weather from the BBC's weather feeds.

To find your location's code go to 

http://www.bbc.co.uk/weather/

and search for your city. The station ID you need is the numeric part at the end of 
URL for the city's weather. For example, a search for London takes you to

http://www.bbc.co.uk/weather/2643743

The StationID is 2643743

This desklet is a fork of Loganj's AccuWeather Desklet,
http://cinnamon-spices.linuxmint.com/desklets/view/10. It makes use of
the marknote xml library: https://code.google.com/p/marknote/